ge":null}],"frontMatter":{"title":"HR Platform: Project Launch","authors":["dev-team"],"tags":["announcement","launch","hr-tech"]},"unlisted":false},"content":"We're thrilled to announce the official launch of the **HR Platform** development project! 🎉\r\n\r\nToday marks the beginning of our journey to build a modern HR Tech solution for workforce management.\r\n\r\n<!-- truncate -->\r\n\r\n## What is HR Platform?\r\n\r\nHR Platform is a comprehensive web portal designed to automate and streamline HR processes for medium and large companies. Our goal is to create a solution that bridges the gap between HR departments and employees, making workforce management efficient and transparent.\r\n\r\n## Project Scope\r\n\r\nThe platform will include:\r\n\r\n### Core Modules\r\n- **👥 Employee Management** - Complete employee lifecycle management\r\n- **📝 Recruitment** - Streamlined hiring process\r\n- **📊 Analytics** - Real-time dashboards and reports\r\n- **🔐 Authentication** - Secure role-based access control\r\n\r\n### Technical Stack\r\n- **Backend**: NestJS with TypeScript\r\n- **Database**: PostgreSQL with TypeORM\r\n- **Authentication**: JWT + Argon2\r\n- **Documentation**: Docusaurus\r\n- **Deployment**: Docker + GitHub Actions\r\n\r\n## Development Timeline\r\n\r\n### Phase 1 (March - April 2026)\r\n- ✅ Project setup and architecture\r\n- ✅ User authentication module\r\n- ✅ Employee CRUD operations\r\n- ✅ API documentation\r\n\r\n### Phase 2 (May - June 2026)\r\n- Recruitment module\r\n- Advanced search and filters\r\n- Email notifications\r\n\r\n### Phase 3 (July - August 2026)\r\n- Analytics dashboard\r\n- Reporting system\r\n- Performance reviews\r\n\r\n## Get Involved\r\n\r\nWe're building in the open! Follow our progress:\r\n\r\n- **GitHub**: [LocalhostLegends/backend](https://github.com/LocalhostLegends/backend)\r\n- **Documentation**: [Check our docs](/docs/intro)\r\n- **Issues**: Report bugs or request features\r\n\r\n## Stay Connected\r\n\r\nThis blog will be updated regularly with:\r\n- Development updates\r\n- New feature announcements\r\n- Technical deep dives\r\n- Release notes\r\n\r\nLet's build something great together! 🚀\r\n\r\n*— HR Platform Team*"}],"blogListPaginated":[{"items":["/2026/03/20/project-launch"],"metadata":{"permalink":"/documentation/blog","page":1,"postsPerPage":10,"totalPages":1,"totalCount":1,"blogDescription":"News, updates, and insights about HR Platform","blogTitle":"HR Platform Blog"}}],"blogTags":{"/documentation/blog/tags/announcement":{"inline":true,"label":"announcement","permalink":"/documentation/blog/tags/announcement","items":["/2026/03/20/project-launch"],"pages":[{"items":["/2026/03/20/project-launch"],"metadata":{"permalink":"/documentation/blog/tags/announcement","page":1,"postsPerPage":10,"totalPages":1,"totalCount":1,"blogDescription":"News, updates, and insights about HR Platform","blogTitle":"HR Platform Blog"}}],"unlisted":false},"/documentation/blog/tags/launch":{"inline":true,"label":"launch","permalink":"/documentation/blog/tags/launch","items":["/2026/03/20/project-launch"],"pages":[{"items":["/2026/03/20/project-launch"],"metadata":{"permalink":"/documentation/blog/tags/launch","page":1,"postsPerPage":10,"totalPages":1,"totalCount":1,"blogDescription":"News, updates, and insights about HR Platform","blogTitle":"HR Platform Blog"}}],"unlisted":false},"/documentation/blog/tags/hr-tech":{"inline":true,"label":"hr-tech","permalink":"/documentation/blog/tags/hr-tech","items":["/2026/03/20/project-launch"],"pages":[{"items":["/2026/03/20/project-launch"],"metadata":{"permalink":"/documentation/blog/tags/hr-tech","page":1,"postsPerPage":10,"totalPages":1,"totalCount":1,"blogDescription":"News, updates, and insights about HR Platform","blogTitle":"HR Platform Blog"}}],"unlisted":false}},"blogTagsListPath":"/documentation/blog/tags","authorsMap":{"dev-team":{"name":"Development Team","title":"HR Platform Team","url":"https://github.com/LocalhostLegends","imageURL":"https://g